{"tid":261472,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養異短問題","createTime":"2017-05-28T13:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T05:18:08.000Z","uid":91228,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d496987c60dfcaf92b7bbdd78c324bf0a0776a","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"小弟對異國短毛貓情有獨鍾<br />\n係金魚街睇襯啲異短會望到唔捨得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得佢地好蠢，好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下各位巴/絲打 𠵱啲貓難唔難養？<br />\n有冇啲特別要注意嘅地方？<br />\n買左返黎要唔要先帶佢去睇獸醫body check 左先？<br />\n如果係金魚街啲寵物店買信唔信得過，會唔會買到啲病貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f5c9f59b72031d57a90dd1e0a986240a6ac877","tid":261472,"uid":77337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:02:07.000Z","msg":"唔難照顧 有野食就嗲到你暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無其他貓咁高'dou' 好似係<br />\n不過異短呢種貓真係好需要經常清潔眼仔"},{"pid":"8e370fd432f80c38d87757046227438993c2439f","tid":261472,"uid":4382,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔難養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過要勤抺眼 因為比其他品種異短係多眼涙分泌 金屬色咁 <br />\n另外注意下佢地呼吸<br />\n鼻仔會唔會太窄 如果太窄要做手術去擴大<br />\n呢類手術對異短好普通 <br />\n我個隻再老啲就要去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附送一張主子圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/003631_dbc1123b292ea7955fd2f445e8a77c91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F003631_dbc1123b292ea7955fd2f445e8a77c91.jpg&h=a4e87fc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"119ae68b04ab2ce35ce3e33ee6bda6632390c09e","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔難照顧 有野食就嗲到你暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無其他貓咁高'dou' 好似係</span><br />\n不過異短呢種貓真係好需要經常清潔眼仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去fd屋企玩過佢隻異短，<br />\n唔識都會嗲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 任你搓圓㩒扁<br />\n屋企已經裝晒貓網，買晒飲水機玩具，差隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83604589c57cdc9e67dd84ec45ceb25b899a9059","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔難養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過要勤抺眼 因為比其他品種異短係多眼涙分泌 金屬色咁 <br />\n另外注意下佢地呼吸<br />\n鼻仔會唔會太窄 如果太窄要做手術去擴大<br />\n呢類手術對異短好普通 <br />\n我個隻再老啲就要去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附送一張主子圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/003631_dbc1123b292ea7955fd2f445e8a77c91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F003631_dbc1123b292ea7955fd2f445e8a77c91.jpg&h=a4e87fc6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你隻主人養到好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你主人係寵物店度買返黎？<br />\n異短除左成日流眼水仲有冇其他病啊？"},{"pid":"aa591403c00827dac4cd7a5e6e05f3a6358e1714","tid":261472,"uid":118810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借post問下關於貓糧既問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家屋企隻異短兩歲幾<br />\n以前尿道有問題 醫生開左處方糧<br />\n食左一年幾 牌子係royal canin<br />\n但上網查過 其實呢個牌子麻麻地<br />\n貓貓老左容易有腎病<br />\n想問下巴絲有冇推薦既牌子 健康既同時尿道又唔會咁易有結石<br />\n唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205cbd0a29c0195d1fabd4a113c3e478e26f3856","tid":261472,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:54:39.000Z","msg":"異短係貓界既智障黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個隻就係一個好例子"},{"pid":"0758b8bc7a056fb7809b576fe551691396971c8b","tid":261472,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T22:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思 借post問下關於貓糧既問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家屋企隻異短兩歲幾<br />\n以前尿道有問題 醫生開左處方糧<br />\n食左一年幾 牌子係royal canin<br />\n但上網查過 其實呢個牌子麻麻地<br />\n貓貓老左容易有腎病<br />\n想問下巴絲有冇推薦既牌子 健康既同時尿道又唔會咁易有結石<br />\n唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉晒全濕糧就得，揀主食罐或者生肉糧<br />\n生石100%同隻貓身體脫水有關，食最靚嗰隻乾糧一樣出事，只要吸收夠水就無問題"},{"pid":"992320f825669e75f0eceed1bb27b426ef1ca553","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>異短係貓界既智障黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個隻就係一個好例子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔智障唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講有啲係蠢到唔識自己食野，要主人餵"},{"pid":"5cb01930849d593d740b58e83f1da878ae6212e9","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"另外想問下，一個月平均開資大約幾錢左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n𠵱啲貓怕唔怕熱？"},{"pid":"d1deebbd531694b16d9e1c9fcb140f3376c67c74","tid":261472,"uid":30568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12d39a799b58740e8171c700c5110937c6b9f018","tid":261472,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/094506_54cbb410d5ece0a9a69dbbe22253b044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F094506_54cbb410d5ece0a9a69dbbe22253b044.jpg&h=d642c84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然我主人都蠢蠢地，但都識做hand hand  同sit嘅動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱買返黎可以同佢去睇次醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢可能會有耳蛩問題同貓癬，不過都係小事黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4440001f580c25018456cfec6569b8f927dcb31","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好去金魚街買 隨時醫藥費仲貴過你買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要買就搵合格嘅貓舍 好嘅breeder<br />\n自家繁殖個啲都唔好揀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n88db網 果啲貓舍信唔信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad89277bf637d356f530ff577fdcd9e48c634446","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/094506_54cbb410d5ece0a9a69dbbe22253b044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F094506_54cbb410d5ece0a9a69dbbe22253b044.jpg&h=d642c84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然我主人都蠢蠢地，但都識做hand hand  同sit嘅動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱買返黎可以同佢去睇次醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢可能會有耳蛩問題同貓癬，不過都係小事黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你果隻個樣好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伸晒條👅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a2ce686079ec6ba05a3d2a04c3cfdfaf44f8ce","tid":261472,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/131328_1f825c410e33cddb6699463a186a4285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F131328_1f825c410e33cddb6699463a186a4285.jpg&h=7844f936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成日都打斜條脷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6a727e6f67ef8404f8a7f9e4d14de6de27eb72","tid":261472,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/094506_54cbb410d5ece0a9a69dbbe22253b044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F094506_54cbb410d5ece0a9a69dbbe22253b044.jpg&h=d642c84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然我主人都蠢蠢地，但都識做hand hand  同sit嘅動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱買返黎可以同佢去睇次醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢可能會有耳蛩問題同貓癬，不過都係小事黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你果隻個樣好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伸晒條👅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢成日覺得自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc43185222f8237b355c28925589ccd97924b25","tid":261472,"uid":60648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好去金魚街買 隨時醫藥費仲貴過你買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要買就搵合格嘅貓舍 好嘅breeder<br />\n自家繁殖個啲都唔好揀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n88db網 果啲貓舍信唔信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢家野真係好睇手神，我呢隻係自家繁殖<br />\n但係都好乖好健康，肯痴人又唔曳，上手又有家教肯自己飲水唔抓傢俬。不過係要成日抹眼仔同梳毛，一日兩三次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xkeoslp5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxkeoslp5&h=1aaed5f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1aa2a31265719aabce91f20958b158e89046d86","tid":261472,"uid":4382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔難養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過要勤抺眼 因為比其他品種異短係多眼涙分泌 金屬色咁 <br />\n另外注意下佢地呼吸<br />\n鼻仔會唔會太窄 如果太窄要做手術去擴大<br />\n呢類手術對異短好普通 <br />\n我個隻再老啲就要去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附送一張主子圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/003631_dbc1123b292ea7955fd2f445e8a77c91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F003631_dbc1123b292ea7955fd2f445e8a77c91.jpg&h=a4e87fc6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你隻主人養到好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你主人係寵物店度買返黎？<br />\n異短除左成日流眼水仲有冇其他病啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係朋友俾我嫁<br />\n我個隻係好貪食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都食唔飽咁 <br />\n其實得眼係佢地最易出問題  如果見異短單眼 眼腫同眼水多一定要載頭罩睇醫生<br />\n扁面狗都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4618db31185d3211dc4b137cc2e0cd07fe192e1","tid":261472,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T08:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8c71e65c3e528f4bb2ba007ce408a591496561","tid":261472,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好去金魚街買 隨時醫藥費仲貴過你買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要買就搵合格嘅貓舍 好嘅breeder<br />\n自家繁殖個啲都唔好揀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n88db網 果啲貓舍信唔信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢家野真係好睇手神，我呢隻係自家繁殖<br />\n但係都好乖好健康，肯痴人又唔曳，上手又有家教肯自己飲水唔抓傢俬。不過係要成日抹眼仔同梳毛，一日兩三次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xkeoslp5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxkeoslp5&h=1aaed5f0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果隻都唔抓傢俬仲成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘乖過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac1149f49d84252674e7195ba1b01d190b65c21","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好去金魚街買 隨時醫藥費仲貴過你買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要買就搵合格嘅貓舍 好嘅breeder<br />\n自家繁殖個啲都唔好揀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n88db網 果啲貓舍信唔信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢家野真係好睇手神，我呢隻係自家繁殖<br />\n但係都好乖好健康，肯痴人又唔曳，上手又有家教肯自己飲水唔抓傢俬。不過係要成日抹眼仔同梳毛，一日兩三次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xkeoslp5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxkeoslp5&h=1aaed5f0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果隻都唔抓傢俬仲成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘乖過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點先養到咁肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打你𠵱隻幾大？<br />\n同埋想問下邊隻牌子嘅貓糧比較好？For 幼貓&amp;成貓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a25f76b2ddd1b415c9d9c27fe914f40062f306","tid":261472,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:37:22.000Z","msg":"巴打你地有冇長開冷氣比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主人一熱就細食好多<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/133718_ed988981717340b24aacaed3dfd84ef5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F133718_ed988981717340b24aacaed3dfd84ef5.jpg&h=86a00f1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66b9507c10c4fcbe0e6ce12698eda96fffb6f30a","tid":261472,"uid":106783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你地有冇長開冷氣比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主人一熱就細食好多<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/133718_ed988981717340b24aacaed3dfd84ef5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F133718_ed988981717340b24aacaed3dfd84ef5.jpg&h=86a00f1a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好得意!!! 邊度可以領養到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f22f593c8c9e4fb105becfdd5ccf4100330cd63","tid":261472,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你地有冇長開冷氣比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主人一熱就細食好多<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/133718_ed988981717340b24aacaed3dfd84ef5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2